---
title: Project Honku
---

<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

    <link rel="shortcut icon" href="public/img/favicon.ico" type="image/x-icon">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-QWTKZyjpPEjISv5WaRU9OFeRpok6YctnYmDr5pNlyT2bRjXh0JMhjY6hW+ALEwIH" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.3/font/bootstrap-icons.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles/index.css">

    <title>{{ title }}</title>
</head>
<body class="bg-light">
    <div id="loading" class="h-100 w-100 bg-black position-fixed top-0 start-0 d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center z-3">
        <img src="public/img/logo.webp" alt="Logo" width="80" style="animation: rotatePlane 1.2s infinite alternate ease-in-out;">
    </div>

    <header class="w-100 h-100 text-white position-relative overflow-hidden bg-color-primary mb-5">
        <div class="container h-100 d-md-flex">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-12 col-md-7 pe-md-5 gy-5 gy-md-0">
                    <div class="left d-flex flex-column justify-content-md-center text-md-start h-100">
                        <h1>こんにちは!</h1>
                        <p>
                            Selamat datang di <b>Project Honku</b>, sebuah organisasi kecil yang berspesialis dalam menerjemahkan
                            visual novel dengan misi untuk memperluas visual novel ke Indonesia dan meningkatkan minat baca bagi pemainnya.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-12 col-md-5 ps-md-5 d-flex align-items-center">
                    <div id="blobs" class="position-relative">
                        <!-- One element must not absolute to fix blob position problem -->
                        <img class="faded" src="public/img/blobs/nekopara.webp" alt="Blob" width="100%" height="auto">
                        <img class="faded position-absolute start-0" src="public/img/blobs/ddlc.webp" alt="Blob" width="100%" height="auto">
                        <img class="faded position-absolute start-0" src="public/img/blobs/sugarsweet.webp" alt="Blob" width="100%" height="auto">

                        <i class="plus bi bi-plus position-absolute"></i>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="position-absolute w-100 bottom-0 start-0 d-flex justify-content-center pb-2">
            <i class="bi bi-chevron-down fs-4"></i>
        </div>
    </header>

    <main>
        <div id="products" class="container mb-5 pb-5 text-center">
            <h3 class="fw-bold mb-4"><span class="text-color-primary">Proyek-proyek</span> kami!</h3>
            <div class="row row-cols-1 row-cols-md-2 row-cols-xl-3 gx-md-3 gy-3 text-start">
                {%- for product in collections.products | sort(attribute="data.status", reverse=true) -%}
                    {% include "product-box.njk" %}
                {%- endfor -%}
            </div>
        </div>

        <div id="team" class="container mb-5 pb-5 text-center">
            <h3 class="fw-bold mb-4"><span class="text-color-primary">Temui tim</span> kami!</h3>
            <div class="row row-cols-1 row-cols-sm-2 row-cols-lg-3 row-cols-xl-4 gx-0 gx-sm-2 gy-2 text-start justify-content-center">
                {% include "teams.njk" %}
            </div>
            <div class="w-100 mt-3 small opacity-50 text-start text-sm-center">
                * Seluruh foto tim dibuat menggunakan Picrew.me oleh kreator 吉田君 dan mematuhi lisensi penggunaan
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-black text-white w-100 mb-5 overflow-hidden">
            <div id="eksplisit" class="container pt-5 pb-5 position-relative">
                <h2 class="fw-bold mb-3">Terkait Konten Eksplisit</h2>
                <p class="mb-0">
                    Kami hanya menerjemahkan visual novel dengan rating family-friendly atau visual novel yang memiliki versi sensor (biasanya versi Steam).
                    <br>
                    Kami tidak akan menerjemahkan visual novel yang menampilkan scene pornografi secara eksplisit seperti eroge.
                    <br><br>
                    Misi kami adalah untuk memudahkan akses visual novel bagi seluruh warga Indonesia sambil tetap berusaha mematuhi <u>Undang-Undang Republik Indonesia Nomor 44 Tahun 2008 tentang Pornografi.</u>
                    <br>
                    Namun, kami mentoleransi beberapa visual novel yang mengandung sindiran seksual yang masih dapat diterima berdasarkan hasil keputusan tim kami.
                </p>

                <span class="position-absolute bottom-0 end-0 lh-1" style="font-size: 15rem; opacity: 15%;">18+</span>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div id="faq" class="container mb-5 text-center">
            <h3 class="fw-bold mb-4"><span class="text-color-primary">Pertanyaan yang</span> sering ditanyakan</h3>
            <div class="row row-cols-1 gy-4">
                {% include "faq.njk" %}
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>

    <footer class="border-top text-white bg-color-primary text-center p-4">
        <img src="public/img/logo.webp" alt="Project Honku" width="60">
        <br>
        © 2024 Project Honku
    </footer>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-YvpcrYf0tY3lHB60NNkmXc5s9fDVZLESaAA55NDzOxhy9GkcIdslK1eN7N6jIeHz" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="scripts/index.js"></script>
</body>
</html>